{
  "texts": [
    "Over time, you start to lash out at people as well, since you have not received negative feedback from lashing out at a humanlike agent.",
    "The risk threshold for relieving your anger at something that will socialize with you is decreased.",
    "You have effectively practiced negative behavior with a humanlike chatbot, which led to you engaging more in that type of negative behavior with humans.",
    "Practice can involve more than negative behaviors.",
    "Suppose you have a friendly, cooperative interaction with an AI, in which you feel safe enough to share your feelings."
  ]
}